{"tid":1667850,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚動物傳心師！！！","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T05:26:06.000Z","uid":247497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ede09d3069c77dd15ff1d4c11c8ca8d6bfddaa56","tid":1667850,"uid":247497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"上次有麻雀俾狗射死左<br />\n今次有鴿食到tg<br />\n仲未計其他動物有受到影響（連警犬都有瀨嘢）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我認為動物傳心師呢個時候就要出黎幫手啦！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最起碼可以同啲動物講返發生咩事<br />\n然後話俾佢地聽香港有好多公廁係有專人服務<br />\n認住個建築物係藍白色<br />\n日日都有人清<br />\n唔去享受下都對唔住自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B33GK_Fjn6U/?igshid=1j3f26z37q0b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB33GK_Fjn6U%2F%3Figshid%3D1j3f26z37q0b5&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=a5639807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB33GK_Fjn6U%2F%3Figshid%3D1j3f26z37q0b5&h=466aa830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B33GK_Fjn6U/?igshid=1j3f26z37q0b5</a><br />\n睇到真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然諗起我地仲有動物傳心師可以幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816179d0e9839f8b989d42a3222f930fe031436c","tid":1667850,"uid":87552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"真係好心痛今晚d警犬...<br />\n赤裸裸食晒煙, 反耳揖尾, 一定出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb70a42c32583941f5d84519dd32f1daa2de64c5","tid":1667850,"uid":295755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手搵辦法推上國際，要求外國永久停止輸出犬隻畀黑警作為警犬用途？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki<br />\n警犬多為德國牧羊犬或者來自荷蘭的比利時瑪連萊犬，另外包括杜賓犬、洛威拿犬、史賓格犬及拉布拉多犬，當中絕大部份來源自荷蘭及比利時。除了從外國引進，警犬隊亦有自行培育繁殖、從香港愛護動物協會挑選、從漁農自然護理署挑選以至由香港市民捐贈（必須為1至2歲大，於退役時，捐贈者具有優先權領養。）。"},{"pid":"6f494ff147d57376e83254e078005152cabdc0c7","tid":1667850,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb70a42c32583941f5d84519dd32f1daa2de64c5","tid":1667850,"uid":295755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手搵辦法推上國際，要求外國永久停止輸出犬隻畀黑警作為警犬用途？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki<br />\n警犬多為德國牧羊犬或者來自荷蘭的比利時瑪連萊犬，另外包括杜賓犬、洛威拿犬、史賓格犬及拉布拉多犬，當中絕大部份來源自荷蘭及比利時。除了從外國引進，警犬隊亦有自行培育繁殖、從香港愛護動物協會挑選、從漁農自然護理署挑選以至由香港市民捐贈（必須為1至2歲大，於退役時，捐贈者具有優先權領養。）。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:55:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">恭喜你，你已經被選中！ <br />\n幫手簽個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫我傳畀十個朋友叫佢簽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-hong-kong-police-force-bringing-police-dog-front-line-while-they-are-usingused-chemical-weapons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-hong-kong-police-force-bringing-police-dog-front-line-while-they-are-usingused-chemical-weapons&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=a3dca8f6\" data